body: ### Welcome to GitHub Pages. This automatic page generator is the easiest way to create beautiful pages for all of your projects. Author your page content here [using GitHub Flavored Markdown](https://guides.github.com/features/mastering-markdown/), select a template crafted by a designer, and publish. After your page is generated, you can check out the new `gh-pages` branch locally. If you’re using GitHub Desktop, simply sync your repository and you’ll see the new branch. ### Authors and Contributors Heres the link to my repository. All files have been upped there. Mighty Drizzle (@dreroc), also /archives on the Drizzzle server. ### Support or Contact Check [documentation](http://drizzzle.in/dreroc/archives).
